examples.en: She stood there winnowing grain all day in the field
examples.ru: Весь день она простояла в поле, провеивая зерно.

examples.en: We need to winnow the list of candidates to three.
examples.ru: Нам нужно сократить список кандидатов до трёх человек.

examples.en: The wind was winnowing her hair.
The winnowing was done by women.
Harvesters winnowed the chaff from the wheat.
